172
00:12:32,218 --> 00:12:34,553
During this season, it's very appropriate,
don't you think?

173
00:12:34,553 --> 00:12:35,721
Ryo!

174
00:12:35,721 --> 00:12:39,925
Then, you stay here by yourself.
I'm going home this time.

175
00:12:39,925 --> 00:12:42,450
All right, whatever.

176
00:12:43,629 --> 00:12:47,833
If I go home now, it will be just
the way Ryo likes it, but...

177
00:12:47,833 --> 00:12:51,496
I'm so scared of ghosts!

178
00:12:52,304 --> 00:12:54,707
What's the matter? Why are you here?

179
00:12:54,707 --> 00:12:57,505
Well, Kaori told me she wants to go home.

180
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,246
Oh, are you going home?

181
00:13:00,246 --> 00:13:02,181
Oh, well, yes.

182
00:13:02,181 --> 00:13:05,017
Since you made up your mind, why don't
you hurry up and go home?

183
00:13:05,017 --> 00:13:06,852
Damn!

184
00:13:06,852 --> 00:13:08,820
Go for it! Go home!

185
00:13:13,592 --> 00:13:16,584
I'm going to stay here too!

186
00:13:17,062 --> 00:13:18,654
Please...

187
00:13:19,431 --> 00:13:21,400
Don't hesitate.

188
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:24,631
If you're here, the ghost will run away.

189
00:13:25,371 --> 00:13:29,175
Well, so much happened today that
I guess you're tired, right?

190
00:13:29,175 --> 00:13:31,544
Let's drink and sleep peacefully tonight.

191
00:13:31,544 --> 00:13:35,414
Don't fill it up like that. I can't drink much.

192
00:13:35,414 --> 00:13:36,711
Oh, don't hesitate.

193
00:13:37,917 --> 00:13:40,286
I know what Ryo's really thinking.

194
00:13:40,286 --> 00:13:43,122
He's going to put Miss Mami to sleep
by getting her drunk

195
